I stayed in one of Cambridge University's colleges - Girton.  This
College is just like Harry Potter's school, with an important
difference:  all the portraits in the big dining hall are portraits
of stern looking women, because Girton used to be a women's college.
This photo shows the dining hall of Girten College, Cambridge (July 17, 2003)<br><br>
